{"tid":1562124,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"咁多位警察，麻煩你地入一入黎。","createTime":"2019-09-12T01:39:37.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-21T03:40:47.000Z","uid":188601,"like":18,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"79c516bb3df73428915f12994e8e785c7632215a","tid":1562124,"uid":188601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T01:39:37.000Z","msg":"首先，多謝大定入左黎。先旨聲明，本人立場為黃，極度反對共產黨。寫呢一篇文，係希望局內既警察諗一諗，之後既事態發展。注意，係局內，即係黑警。<br />\n<br />\n上星期日讀到梁芷珊小姐既一個post，突然有感而發，希望藉此透其作出延伸閱讀。內容如下：<br />\n<br />\n事到如今，我唯一仍尊重警察嘅，係你哋無人割席，仲係好團結，呢方面你哋好高質素。所以，我哋呢邊都唔會割席，因為我哋香港人都好高質素。<br />\n<br />\n係呢到，我好同意。我好欣賞既警察既團結，你地無人割席。所以第一個情況係：恭喜你，共產黨，林鄭贏左，你地贏左。林鄭一定論功行賞。<br />\n眾所週知，你知，我知，只係新聞報導唔知，今次鎮壓既最大功勞係解放軍同黑社會，佢地唔理港人死活，不斷使用強暴，傷人，斬人，輕傷，重傷，死人？比比皆是。跟住落黎，解放軍全面進場，取締香港警隊，二哥，游乃強，李偉文，謝振中，江，何君堯呢班人全部升官發財，而大眾既警察只會繼續為呢班黑警，講大話唔斬眼既上司效命。升職無你份，流血流汗有你份，為解放軍效忠有你份。你地係唔係真係真心，為何君堯，游乃強呢d&rdquo;精人出口，笨人出手&lsquo;既人效命？點解唔可以獨立調查？點解唔可以交出cctv？我真係好希望你地諗一諗。<br />\n注意係呢到，我想帶出多一個message，我出到黎眼見有好多好警察，高eq，維護警民關係。係呢到，我絕無意幫黑警洗白，但大前提係&rsquo;黑&rsquo;警。都係個句，無一個黑警係無辜，黑警死全家，黑警還眼。好希望咁多位白警，你地諗一諗，記住，希望咁多位白警恥與為伍，希望你地唔好比黑警，黑社會同你拉上關係。東家唔打打西家。<br />\n<br />\n第二個情況，係你地唔想發生既，林鄭輸左，共產黨輸左。獨立調查成立，係呢到，我都唔想打落去。結局一定係全面清算警隊，黑警無一幸免，白警蒙受不白之冤，從此警民永久破裂。輕則無左份工，重則自己諗。<br />\n<br />\n我絕對明白樹大有枯枝，但而家枯左既係條樹幹，黑警當道，希望咁多位警察諗一諗，割席唔割席，贏左輸左既後果。<br />\n<br />\n最後，我想點名兩個人，一個係我中學同學，遲左份工，上左前線，一個係我輔警朋友，六月開始無番輔警，支持獨立調查。<br />\n<br />\n真係最後，<br />\n<br />\n光復香港，時代革命。<br />\n五大訴求，缺人不可。"},{"pid":"c0bb6ff0b870856568427c8529bb4ebd19f29f42","tid":1562124,"uid":76702,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T01:40:13.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"40b819b4642413f40289c8bfeff9040b03f7c8ff","tid":1562124,"uid":123991,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T01:40:19.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />出黎呀 自由閪！ <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div></strong></span></span><br />\n<strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />五大訴求 缺一不可 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></div></strong><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aPJ3iwW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaPJ3iwW.png&h=bd74ec1d&s={SIZE}\" /></div>"},{"pid":"a772c10c2ea9154cd8922312406e3dc3146a1bd7","tid":1562124,"uid":58958,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T01:41:04.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: teal;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>叫阿爺阿嫲阿公阿婆阿爸阿媽投</strong></span></span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n【保民聯】建制保皇 建設保民 香港值得更好的建設派<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1560300\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1560300</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2edu5dD.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2edu5dD.png&h=f7e4a997&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c5d1cf843b7522b6ac78c7ac551d63a166750624","tid":1562124,"uid":188601,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T01:51:30.000Z","msg":"記住，香港既繁榮穩定，係因為佢係一個自由發展，配合法治既社會。兩者缺一不可。白警，唔好再因爲黑警，唔敢同人講你做警察，唔好再因黑警，休班都拎gear，唔好再因該黑警，令到個仔無朋友。"},{"pid":"3a147a638ee547f3fb0d5dbf8933025f9f3556a3","tid":1562124,"uid":188601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T02:00:55.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"259a2b5f00e94ad8a7921d2aecb5d9a55fc0143f","tid":1562124,"uid":188601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T02:03:31.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"135367b13ced7a5c21edb8a618baedca706955f6","tid":1562124,"uid":188601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T02:05:59.000Z","msg":"推到比警察睇到"},{"pid":"6e86c10cde986711ffb8123a7eacd9013ea1313d","tid":1562124,"uid":188601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T02:07:41.000Z","msg":"推到比警察睇到"},{"pid":"b66fb50e8dec0f8660842c51f9af428d1cb254b3","tid":1562124,"uid":188601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T02:09:55.000Z","msg":"光復香港，時代革命"},{"pid":"b9aa94e8883e6ddd7aef0114967aa08374fed04b","tid":1562124,"uid":188601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T02:10:39.000Z","msg":"光復香港，時代革命"},{"pid":"72f1d64b0640db3a5d87218ae5de9b0c3b4b4ff2","tid":1562124,"uid":188601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T02:16:04.000Z","msg":"光復香港，時代革命"},{"pid":"9cbe34e454eae46ac53164696f6a4ee5bd943dff","tid":1562124,"uid":188601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T02:20:45.000Z","msg":"光復香港，時代革命"},{"pid":"fa14760a2add2995207290a3fe310aafd4a06526","tid":1562124,"uid":188601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T02:21:34.000Z","msg":"有黑警比負評。希望你地唔好拖累白警"},{"pid":"9f7ad6b05d2fd91ccec67253264c3558a964c434","tid":1562124,"uid":188601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T03:01:41.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"fd946db7e6e83abaa378a44ce51479b4d459a451","tid":1562124,"uid":188601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T04:06:09.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8406c1a3058d291f405a99b50570f4d8682d84db","tid":1562124,"uid":188601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T04:20:00.000Z","msg":"自推十連"},{"pid":"df4de27343def6d9cd36fbc0360628829d4c412c","tid":1562124,"uid":188601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T05:36:54.000Z","msg":"推撚爆佢"},{"pid":"12f03a735b860332a18e029f2807dce4809b53c3","tid":1562124,"uid":188601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T07:36:02.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ff76bcc701ebac14a7fc273c40e914c15a22b65b","tid":1562124,"uid":188601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T11:05:02.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f1a607a8cf52ee050280ed845be77de97096344f","tid":1562124,"uid":188601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T12:37:51.000Z","msg":"推撚爆佢"},{"pid":"23c986fd1365cc93cc781d7f85373ee9ac531831","tid":1562124,"uid":188601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T13:03:52.000Z","msg":"推撚爆佢"},{"pid":"bf937416ebae9430b563231f56e34763874fbcb7","tid":1562124,"uid":188601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T09:18:00.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"36629e3bf86c9f0f18120370e99a13085b2d2c5e","tid":1562124,"uid":188601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T00:05:12.000Z","msg":"推撚爆佢"},{"pid":"e447180e59b5ef7559a02bd3e35ffeb42b06e120","tid":1562124,"uid":219536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T00:05:40.000Z","msg":"推"}]}